data.description: Welcome to this 3 bed ranch home with an oversized 1 car garage in Lincoln Village South/Woodlawn neighborhood! As you walk up to the home, you are welcomed by the front porch overlooking a fenced in front yard. The home has been well maintained. The roof was entirely replaced in 2018 and insulation added to the attic. All windows were replaced in 2019 and have a transferable warranty. Kitchen appliances have also been updated and mechanicals are in great condition. There are beautiful hardwood floors underneath the carpet in the hallway and the back two bedrooms. The backyard is huge and fully fenced in! You will be in close proximity to shopping, restaurants, and more! If you are looking for a rental, this meets the 1% rule. Schedule a tour today!
